article.description: — Neemias Queta registered 14 points and five blocks as Utah State beat Fresno State 69-53 on Thursday night.
article.headline: Queta scores 14 to lift Utah St. over Fresno St. 69-53
article.linkText: Queta scores 14 to lift Utah St. over Fresno St. 69-53
article.story: FRESNO, Calif. -- — Neemias Queta registered 14 points and five blocks as Utah State beat Fresno State 69-53 on Thursday night. Alphonso Anderson had 13 points for Utah State (14-5, 11-2 Mountain West Conference). Steven Ashworth added 10 points. Orlando Robinson had six assists for the Bulldogs (7-7, 5-7). ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
